main event: A civilian reported an unidentified flying object sighting in Memphis, Tennessee on October 12, 1969.
interesting points: The report was part of Project Blue Book, which investigated UFO sightings., The sighting occurred at 2015Z (GMT) and had one unidentified object., The conclusion of the investigation noted insufficient data to take further action., The witness indicated that they had not seen a similar phenomenon before, but another person was with them during the sighting., The report lacks any photographs or physical evidence and remains officially closed.
witness description: a male civilian and another individual who did not see the object
